          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "核心线索：差异即进位",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>观察题目给出的量</strong>：题目给了“加法和 ($v$)”和“异或和 ($u$)”。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>联想公式</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$A + B = (A \\oplus B) + 2(A \\& B)$$\n移项得到：\n$$(A + B) - (A \\oplus B) = 2(A \\& B)$$",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "即：<strong>加法和 - 异或和 = 2 倍的进位部分</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "题目给了 $Sum$ 和 $Xor$，就是在暗示你去处理这个“差值”。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>判定无解</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "根据公式可知，$v - u$ 不能为 <strong>0</strong> 和 <strong>奇数</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "该如何构造？（保底构造形式）",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>公式提醒我们要在意差值</strong> $diff = v - u$ <strong>。</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>满足 Xor 是最容易的</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "要想异或和为 $u$，最简单的办法就是数组里直接放一个 $u$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "此时：数组 $[u]$，异或和 $= u$（满足），加法和 $= u$（不满足，缺 $v-u$）。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>凑 Sum 但不破坏 Xor</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们需要往数组里塞进数值 $v-u$，但不能改变异或和。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在异或的世界里，什么东西是“透明”的？是 <strong>0</strong>。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "怎么用非 0 的数凑出 0？利用 $x \\oplus x = 0$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>贪心保底形式构造</strong>",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们需要加上的数值是 $diff = v - u$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们把它拆成两个 $x$，使得 $x + x = diff$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "这样一来，我们在数组里放入两个 $x$：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>对加法的贡献</strong>：$+x+x$，即补足了差值。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>对异或的贡献</strong>：$\\oplus x \\oplus x$，即 $\\oplus 0$，毫无影响。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "所以，$[u, \\frac{v-u}{2}, \\frac{v-u}{2}]$ 这个<strong>保底形式</strong>就自然诞生了。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "更短的构造形式（长度为 2）",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "根据公式推导，我们必然得到：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$a \\& b = \\frac{v - u}{2} = x$$\n假设存在任意一对数 $[a, b]$ 满足题目要求：\n现在我们来分析**二进制位**的冲突情况：\n**关键矛盾**：\n**结论**：\n**长度为 2 的构造形式：** $[u+x, x]$",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll u, v; cin >> u >> v;\n\tll cha = v - u;\n\n\tif (cha & 1 or cha < 0) {\n\t\tcout << -1 << endl;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\n\tif (cha == 0) {\n\t\tif (u == 0)cout << 0 << endl;\n\t\telse cout << 1 << endl << u << endl;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\n\tll x = cha / 2;\n\tif ((u & x) == 0) {\n\t\tcout << 2 << endl;\n\t\tcout << (u + x) << ' ' << x << endl;\n\t}\n\telse {\n\t\tcout << 3 << endl;\n\t\tcout << u << ' ' << x << ' ' << x << endl;\n\t}\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
